description.text:
(Almost) everything you need to play Micropul (<a rel="nofollow" href="http://neutralbox.com/micropul" >http://neutralbox.com/micropul</a>) with 1 to 3 players!
&quot;Micropul is an abstract strategy tile-laying game. It is usually played as a 2-player game in which players take turn placing tiles and stones, stocking new tiles and claiming groups. Micropul can also be played as a solitaire puzzle where the goal is to play optimally and beat your previous score.&quot;
<b >Update (6/8/2012):</b> The tiles should interlock now. At least, my test prints do. I still haven't tried printing a full set yet.
